posts.subject: Peak Israel, Peak Empire
Youtube has a right to censor their system....
posts.body:
I don't think anyone will like the results if the government tries to act as an arbiter here.....

But the minute any company does edit content - ALL of their content should become available for frivolous lawsuits (as our system allows).  They should lose all free speech protections.

In addition, any employee of censoring companies should consider themselves "fair game" by those who simply want them dead. It's reasonable to assume that behaviors have now reached a threshold where political assassination becomes commonplace. We're just waiting for first steps now. Once the killing starts - it will become normalized.

Hopefully only the true Karens will perish....but everyone knows that won't always be the case. This is what happens when groups just don't wish to share the same world.

Google should be very concerned if someone gets their hands on a nuke. They are a target rich environment. A huge temptation.

Live and let live was  a safety valve. It's gone now. And there are soooo many people who need killing.

I don't believe Google is ready for this. Their imagination just doesn't stretch that far. Others are ready for Karen extermination. Over time, it will become routine for them. Extermination of pests - and lines of pests.

A civil society minds it's own business.
